
This code was initially devloped to fit the CCN spectra as a function of wind speed, temperature
and pressure. The R scripts are located in the R/ccn folder. It makes use of series of R functions
listed in the R/functions_met directory 

I would appreciate feedback from users of this package.  Please suggest comments,
suggestions, and issue reports to https://github.com/prabshr/ccnFits.git

Author Contact: Prabhakar Shrestha
                pshrestha@uni-bonn.de

Use of the software:

The authors name and the git repository should be appropriately cited for any use of this software.
 
